#compdef mlx
# Documentation: https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-19
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.
# STUB: MLX (ml-explore/mlx) is a Python/C++/Swift array framework for Apple
# silicon and does not ship a top-level "mlx" command. Per-subtool CLIs live in
# the mlx-lm package (mlx_lm.generate, mlx_lm.convert, mlx_lm.lora, etc.) and
# have their own completion files. Keeping minimal fallback so #compdef matches
# bin name if one ever appears.

_arguments -s \
  '(- *)'{-h,--help}'[show help]' \
  '(- *)'{-v,--version}'[show version]' \
  '*:: :_default'
